	 				<h2>Information display</h2>
	 				<p>I am interested in improving the display and dissemination of scientific information. This curiousity has also extended into an interest in interactive displays. I use Arduino hardware, and <a href="http://processing.org">Processing</a> to create displays that respond to their environment.</p>
